summary: Elvish relatives is a New mod just out that adds a village next to riverwood but it is not just regular nords in the village no it is not , it is Wood elves! Yes Wood elves
descriptionHtml:
Elvish relatives is a New mod just out that adds a village next to riverwood but it is not just regular nords in the village no it is not , it is Wood elves! Yes Wood elves.

The mod is currently in Beta version 1.0 

I just wanted to release it so people could come up with idea\\\'s that they would like Like quests, New weapons etc 

So i would greatly appreciate feed back and don\\\'t expect it to be ultra amazing already I just released it so people could have a look at my first mod idea and there is alot of fixes to be done currently i just want you guys to come up with some idea\\\'s if you would like to \\\"COLABERATE WITH ME\\\" please contact me via skype : xrambozhd and we shall talk then other than that good bye the mod will generally from now be updated weekly!
author: Premeo
